App
”) operated by radio.de GmbH, Mühlenkamp 59, 22303 Hamburg, Germany (hereinafter also referred to as “
radio.de
”, “
we
” and “
us
”). The protection of your personal data is an important matter to radio.de when collecting and processing such data while using our App.
